| c1   | c3   | c1 + c3 |
+------+------+---------+
|    1 |    3 |       4 |
+------+------+---------+
EXPLAIN BASIC select c1 from (select distinct c1, rand() from t1) v;
Query Plan
=============================
|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME|
-----------------------------
|0 |SUBPLAN SCAN       |v   |
|1 |└─HASH DISTINCT    |    |
|2 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|t1  |
=============================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([v.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([v.c1])
  1 - output([t1.c1], [rand()]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      distinct([t1.c1], [rand()])
  2 - output([t1.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([t1.c1]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=false, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([t1.__pk_increment]), range(MIN ; MAX)always true
select c1 from (select distinct c1, rand() from t1) v;
+------+
| c1   |
+------+
|    1 |
|    1 |
+------+
